Page Name Rules for ACM Online Judge
====================================

/home               Home
/sets               Problem Sets (just render variable `problem-sets' as Markdown)
/problems           All Problems
    ?page=          > 页数从1开始，每页显示题目数目为 Variable[problems-per-page]
    &author=        > 如果不为空则按该作者过滤（注意不是owner）
/submit             Submit
    ?problem=
/status             Status
    ?top=           > 列出从该号码开始的records，每页显示数目为 Variable[records-per-page]
    &owner=
    &problem=
    &language=      > 按语言过滤，比如 c cpp java
    &verdict=       > 按结果过滤，比如 ac  wa  ce，URL的query里放的是数字
/reports            Reports
/dashboard          Dashboard
/problem            Read Problem
    ?id=
/record             View Record
    ?id=
/report             View Report
    ?id=
/new/report         Create Report
/remove/report      Remove Report
/show/problem       Show Problem (Enable)
/hide/problem       Hide Problem (Disable)
/rejudge            Rejudge Record
/add/permission     Add Permission
/remove/permission  Remove Permission
/set/variable       Set Variable
